@startuml High School Story — Stat System

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor #F0FFF4
    BorderColor #276749
    FontSize 11
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FFFBEB
    BorderColor #D69E2E
    FontSize 10
}

title Stat System — Overview

class "Core Stats" as CoreStats {
    Energy    : 0–100
    Stress    : 0–100
    Mood      : 0–100
    --
    Each decays daily at end of day.
    Restored by sleep, food, activities.
}

class "Knowledge Stats" as KnowledgeStats {
    Math           : 0–100
    English        : 0–100
    History        : 0–100
    Science        : 0–100
    Art            : 0–100
    Music          : 0–100
    PhysicalEd     : 0–100
    -- Year 2+ electives --
    Psychology     : 0–100
    Programming    : 0–100
    Literature     : 0–100
    CreativeWriting: 0–100
    -- Year 3+ electives --
    Philosophy     : 0–100
    Drama          : 0–100
    Journalism     : 0–100
    CareerPrep     : 0–100
}

class "Academic Performance" as AcademicPerf {
    midtermScore  : computed
    finalScore    : computed
    yearGrade     : PASS / FAIL
    --
    Computed from relevant Knowledge stats
    weighted by subject schedule hours.
    Failure = game over (autosave rollback).
}

class "Relationship Scores" as RelScores {
    npcId : String
    score : 0–100
    stage : 1–6
    --
    One entry per NPC.
    Affects dialogue options,
    event access, endings.
}

class "Inventory" as Inv {
    slots      : limited (backpack capacity)
    items[]    : Item
    currency   : Int
}

class "Item" as ItemClass {
    name     : String
    type     : Consumable | Gift | KeyItem
    effect   : StatModifier?
    --
    Consumables: used in dorm or (risky) in class.
    Gifts: given to NPCs for Rel. gain.
    Key items: story triggers or passive effects.
}

' Decay rules
note top of CoreStats
    **Daily Decay (end of day):**
    Energy   –20 per day (restored by sleep: +60)
    Stress   +5 per school day (–10 on weekends)
    Mood     –5 per day unless boosted by activity

    **Floor / ceiling effects:**
    Energy ≤ 20 → classroom action effectiveness –50%
    Stress ≥ 80 → Mood decay doubles, study efficiency –30%
    Mood ≤ 20  → NPC interactions give –50% Rel. gain
end note

' Knowledge gain sources
note right of KnowledgeStats
    **Knowledge gain sources:**
    Study action in class: +2–5 (subject)
    Participate action: +5–10, Stress +2
    Homework / Self-Study period: +1–3
    Study with NPC: +3–6 (that NPC's proficient subjects)
    Reading off-topic book: +1 (unrelated subject)

    **Knowledge decay:**
    No automatic decay.
    Knowledge is permanent once earned.
end note

note right of AcademicPerf
    **Exam calculation:**
    Midterm: avg of relevant Knowledge * 0.4
    Final:   avg of relevant Knowledge * 0.6
    Cumulative score determines PASS/FAIL.

    FAIL → game over.
    Autosave rollback options:
      1 week before / 1 month / 3 months.
end note

CoreStats       -->  AcademicPerf   : Energy/Stress affect study efficiency
KnowledgeStats  -->  AcademicPerf   : feeds exam scores
Inv             -->  CoreStats      : consumables modify stats
Inv             -->  RelScores      : gifts modify NPC scores
RelScores       -->  CoreStats      : NPC proximity mood bonus
ItemClass       --o  Inv

@enduml
